    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you're saying \"methods of addressing social issues\" as if there's even a real debate about whether the goals are right. like, if the goal is equality, isn't anyone who calls it \"censorship\" just trying to shut down the conversation? if you had to pick, do you think the \"woke\" movement is actually making progress on justice, or is the pushback against it a necessary part of protecting free speech?",
